  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creators of Synth Riders comes <strong>FINAL FURY</strong>, a VR fighting game that redefines stepping into the ring. Face off against the galaxy’s fiercest fighters—offline or across the world with rollback netcode. This isn’t some button-pushing battle. Every punch, every block, and every special attack is powered by YOU.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FINAL FURY</strong> is more than a fighting game—this is a<strong> VR</strong> fighting game done right, with the support from the nine-time EVO champion Justin Wong!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‎ㅤ</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/9d566eb6e1763e2f6c360f7023ba0816.poster.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/9d566eb6e1763e2f6c360f7023ba0816.webm?t=1772842639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/7bbcf2cb17e50262c8d7757e9ea992fa.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Feel like a fighter</strong> as YOU step into the arena. It’s a first-person throw-down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Innovative VR combat</strong>, blends classic fighting mechanics with physical gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Seven characters and counting</strong>, each with unique moves to match your play style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Advised by Justin Wong</strong> and inspired by arcade legends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Arcade Mode</strong> with challenging AI and unlockable rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Compete Online</strong> with cross-platform play and rollback netcode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Heart-pumping OST</strong> composed by Zardonic (SUPERHOT: Mind Control Delete).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Break a Sweat</strong> while delivering a beatdown!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/62d1b84975d2923daa09e15d7910965b.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/f5a553b68100d324a83c1e21dee2ac0a.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FINAL FURY</strong> isn’t just about picking a fighter and learning their moves—BECOME the fighter! Feel the adrenaline as you unleash your FINAL FURY in immersive VR battles where you are the hero. Whether you’re rushing down, footsie-ing, or action-canceling your way to victory, <strong>FINAL FURY</strong>’s skill curve is easy to pick up and tough to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/116ae908672bf5fc87aff3e725974675.poster.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/116ae908672bf5fc87aff3e725974675.webm?t=1772842639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/83155364f2e2fad6896553ea644bff1e.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience fierce fights while coming to blows in first person, then get pumped as ground-pounding finishers and grapples unfold in cinematic third-person perspective cuts. All this explodes around you while battling to the adrenaline-soaked soundtrack from Zardonic (SUPERHOT: MIND CONTROL DELETE)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/3d62f0a137c7990d5a6db285f77668a9.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the official<strong> FINAL FURY</strong> Discord to learn more about community tournaments, the latest FINAL FURY news, and insights straight from the dev team! This fight’s just getting started!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/4b3d440b3a6e4bb311cf6c5c6abb28c0.webp?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creators of Synth Riders comes <strong>FINAL FURY</strong>, a VR fighting game that redefines stepping into the ring. Face off against the galaxy’s fiercest fighters—offline or across the world with rollback netcode. This isn’t some button-pushing battle. Every punch, every block, and every special attack is powered by YOU.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FINAL FURY</strong> is more than a fighting game—this is a<strong> VR</strong> fighting game done right, with the support from the nine-time EVO champion Justin Wong!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‎ㅤ</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/9d566eb6e1763e2f6c360f7023ba0816.poster.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/9d566eb6e1763e2f6c360f7023ba0816.webm?t=1772842639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1782760/extras/7bbcf2cb17e50262c8d7757e9ea992fa.avif?t=1772842639\" width=616 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Feel like a fighter</strong> as YOU step into the arena. It’s a first-person throw-down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Innovative VR combat</strong>, blends classic fighting mechanics with physical gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Seven characters and counting</strong>, each with unique moves to match your play style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Advised by Justin Wong</strong> and inspired by arcade legends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥊 <strong>Arcade Mode</strong> with challenging AI and unlockable rewards.</p><p 